# learnpytorch

Minimal PyTorch setup with unit tests (no notebooks).

## Setup (uv)

```bash
uv venv --python 3.12
source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Run tests

```bash
uv run pytest
```
